(105, '-hngbil, -hngbil, -bil', 'suffix', 'plural', 'plural', '', '', 'for all trees; also plural for some topographical nouns, the longer allophone is more common, with the loss of the final consonant (if any) of the stem; there is no consonant loss with  -bil.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
